#. Translators : DO NOT TRANSLATE the ${SEAT_DAEMON_STATUS} variable name
#: ../solaar.templates:15
msgid "Use plugdev group?"
msgstr "Koristi plugdev grupu?"

#. Description
#: ../solaar.templates:15
msgid ""
"Please specify how non-root users should be given access to the Logitech "
"receiver devices."
msgstr ""
"Odredite kako će nekorijenski korisnici imati pristup uređajima Logitechovih "
"prijemnika."

#. Description
#: ../solaar.templates:15
msgid ""
"If systemd or consolekit are in use, they can apply ACLs to make them "
"accessible via Solaar for the user logged in on the current seat. Right now, "
"${SEAT_DAEMON_STATUS} daemon is running."
msgstr ""
"Ako se koriste systemd ili consolekit, oni mogu primijeniti ACL-ove kako bi "
"mogli biti dostupni putem Solaara za korisnike prijavljene u trenutnu "
"sesiju. Trenutno je, ${SEAT_DAEMON_STATUS} pozadinski program pokrenut."

#. Description
#: ../solaar.templates:15
msgid ""
"If neither of these daemons is in use, or if the receiver should also be "
"accessible for remotely logged in users, it is possible to grant access for "
"members of the \"plugdev\" system group."
msgstr ""
"Ako se nijedan od tih pozadinskih programa ne koristi, ili ako bi prijemnik "
"trebao biti dostupan putem udaljene prijave, moguće je dopustiti pristup "
"članovima 'plugdev' grupe sustava."

#. Description
#: ../solaar.templates:15
msgid ""
"If you do use the \"plugdev\" group, don't forget to make sure all the "
"appropriate users are members of that group. You can add new members to the "
"group by running, as root:\n"
"    adduser <username> plugdev\n"
"For the group membership to take effect, the affected users need to log out "
"and back in again."
msgstr ""
"Ako koristite 'plugdev' grupu, pobrinite se da su svi odgovarajući korisnici "
"članovi te grupe. Možete dodati novog člana u grupu pokretanjem korijenskog "
"korisnika (root):\n"
"    adduser <korisnikovo ime> plugdev\n"
"Kako bi članstvo grupe postalo aktivno, dodani korisnik se mora odjaviti i "
"ponovno prijaviti u sustav."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "By default, the Logitech receiver devices are only accessible by the root "
